'Plant Site Selection for Recycling Plants of Waste Electrical and Electronic Equipment in Turkey by Using Multicriteria Decision Making Methods'
I have used the data available in this paper to find the relevant ranking of cities for a recycling palnt in Turkey.
The paper is available at: 
